16
00:03:41,890 --> 00:03:45,030
I want to put the blame on someone, but there's no one to blame.

17
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:49,730
Even if I explode and tell my mom that it's all her fault, it only hurts my heart more.

18
00:03:49,730 --> 00:03:52,990
