20
00:03:55,260 --> 00:04:01,070
I know, right? I only told her to apologize to Shi Hyun.

21
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:07,290
How can Soo Ji do that to me? Should I just reveal everything to her, right now?

22
00:04:07,290 --> 00:04:09,690
"Shi Hyun got even more hurt because of you."

23
00:04:09,690 --> 00:04:15,130
Yes! Tell her everything. Just reveal it to her and let her get hurt, too.

24
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:21,790
No. That doesn't solve anything and that's not something I would do, either.

25
00:04:21,790 --> 00:04:24,360
You're the one who got hurt!

26
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:28,580
You should've just leaned onto Kwon Shi Hyun and cried it all out.

27
00:04:30,370 --> 00:04:32,800
If Shi Hyun had never met me,

28
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:36,870
