29
00:04:36,870 --> 00:04:40,780
Forget it. Just think about yourself now. Just yourself.

30
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:46,570
Kyung Joo, what should I do?

31
00:04:48,900 --> 00:04:53,720
It'll all pass. Everything will pass.

32
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:59,740
When? When will it get better?

33
00:04:59,740 --> 00:05:02,660
When will it not hurt anymore?

34
00:05:02,660 --> 00:05:06,510
If I knew the answer, I would be able to endure it,

35
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:09,740
