36
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:26,950
Soo Ji! Soo Ji, open the door! Soo Ji!

37
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:35,350
What's wrong, Soo Ji?

38
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:47,850
Let's go home. If not, should we go to the hospital?

39
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:54,370
I don't want to. I don't want to see my mom.

40
00:05:54,370 --> 00:05:57,440
I don't want to go home, either.

41
00:05:57,440 --> 00:06:00,040
I don't want to see anyone.

42
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:08,220
I want to disappear from this world.

43
00:06:14,700 --> 00:06:16,950
Can you turn off the lights?

44
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,910
You were right.

45
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:32,130
Shi Hyun left.

46
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:35,090
We can't return to our old selves.

47
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:44,530
- Se Joo.
- Yeah?

48
00:06:44,530 --> 00:06:46,480
Se Joo.

49
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:52,310
Are you...

50
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:56,870
