55
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:44,470
♫ In case I got farther away from her I must have been hesitating ♫

56
00:07:44,470 --> 00:07:52,580
♫ I should've said I love you first ♫

57
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:56,830
♫ I should've said I was in love with you ♫

58
00:07:56,830 --> 00:08:00,760
