♫ I should've approached you first ♫

62
00:08:19,670 --> 00:08:25,880
I'll at least make you feel less lonely than how it was when the three of us were together.

63
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:28,860
I won't make you lonely.

64
00:08:28,860 --> 00:08:32,820
I'll stay by your side, Choi Soo Ji.

65
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,050
Thanks.

66
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:46,030
[2018 National Arts College Entrance Exam]

67
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:57,740
There's nothing easy about this.

68
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:03,170
