70
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:13,880
In our house, we never allow people who speak of useless things.

71
00:09:13,890 --> 00:09:15,700
What do you mean?

72
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:22,010
The day Shi Hyun's mother passed away, the things you told my daughter-in-law,

73
00:09:22,010 --> 00:09:26,340
I don't know if others do, but I know.

74
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:33,370
You may not have known that things would turn out the way they did, but words said out of greed are a way of showing anger.

75
00:09:33,370 --> 00:09:39,990
