76
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:54,990
Yes, Director Myeong, this is Shi Hyun. Can you meet me at the hospital for a bit?

77
00:09:54,990 --> 00:09:58,460
I was thinking about taking the day off today.

78
00:09:59,690 --> 00:10:03,250
