79
00:10:03,250 --> 00:10:05,680
Then I'll go to your house.

80
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:10,780
Are you not feeling very well?

81
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:14,270
No, I just wanted to rest for a day.

82
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:19,520
Soo Ji must have gone to school.

83
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,790
Yeah.

84
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:27,240
But why did you ask to meet me?

85
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:33,570
I will just ask you directly.

86
00:10:33,570 --> 00:10:38,660
Why did you lie to me?

87
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:42,550
You told me that my mother was the driver of the hit-and-run accident.

88
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:45,400
Shi Hyun, about that...

89
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:49,130
It was also you, who told my mom to go to Jeongeup.

90
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:54,410
It's as I suspected.

91
00:10:55,420 --> 00:10:59,190
