97
00:11:30,490 --> 00:11:32,480
Shi Hyun... it's just that...

98
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:38,470
I... just found out about the vice chairman going to Jeongeup coincidentally.

99
00:11:38,470 --> 00:11:42,990
I just mentioned it to her because she was worried about it.

100
00:11:42,990 --> 00:11:49,240
Alright. I will acknowledge that I was being unnecessarily nosy.

101
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:51,220
I'm sorry.

102
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:57,400
But it was her decision to go there.

103
00:11:57,400 --> 00:12:01,250
I was worried about her, so I set everything aside and followed her.

104
00:12:01,260 --> 00:12:03,110
And then...

105
00:12:04,950 --> 00:12:07,310
you hit Tae Hee.

106
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:15,950
If you have a conscience, please stop here. I won't tell Soo Ji or my father.

107
00:12:15,950 --> 00:12:17,680
Soo Ji...

108
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:21,140
She really won't be able to handle it.

109
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,910
