111
00:13:40,860 --> 00:13:42,680
Mom...

112
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:49,530
Can you not go to work? Are you still ill?

113
00:13:49,530 --> 00:13:52,060
I'm just going to rest for a day.

114
00:13:53,790 --> 00:13:57,720
Did you stay out overnight? Where were you?

115
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:06,900
After going to the hospital yesterday, I went to orchestra practice again. I'm going to sleep for a bit and go back to school.

116
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:10,670
You should rest.

117
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:34,550
I never doubted you, but I wanted to confirm it with my own eyes.

118
00:14:34,550 --> 00:14:37,300
You don't resent me, right?
[DNA One and DNA Two match 99.98%]

119
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:50,770
Just from who

120
00:14:50,770 --> 00:14:54,310
