176
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:46,040
It's hard for me if you keep being like this.

177
00:21:46,040 --> 00:21:48,480
I'm not doing this to return to how we were before.

178
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:50,680
Then, why are you like this?

179
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:56,860
Tae Hee... come home.

180
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:04,260
I'll take care of it. Why do you care?

181
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:09,310
I know it's because of me, so that's why you're not going home and staying uncomfortably elsewhere.

182
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:18,030
You should go home for your own good. Then, I won't bother you anymore.

183
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:40,140
