184
00:22:40,140 --> 00:22:43,170
Since you want to major in drawing, you should try to get into an art school.

185
00:22:43,170 --> 00:22:47,530
If you're interested in other things like designing, it's better to apply to a general college.

186
00:22:47,530 --> 00:22:50,490
I didn't think about it that widely yet.

187
00:22:50,490 --> 00:22:52,760
When are you thinking about applying?

188
00:22:52,760 --> 00:22:54,980
As soon as possible.

189
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:59,140
Why are you thinking about leaving all of a sudden?

190
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:03,860
I need to go to an unfamiliar place to forget about some complicated things.

191
00:23:03,860 --> 00:23:07,180
I also thought that I'd think about new things.

192
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:12,730
Alright. If you need any more help, just tell me.

193
00:23:12,730 --> 00:23:14,580
Thank you.

194
00:23:15,500 --> 00:23:18,530
I was always thankful towards you, Ahjussi.

195
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:21,900
What are you saying all of a sudden?

196
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:27,260
Here. These are all the practice books and memos I used when I started playing the cello. It'll be helpful to you.

197
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:33,720
Wow. Why are you giving me this, Unni? Are you going somewhere?

198
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:38,370
Just because. I want you to do well if you end up wanting to learn to play the cello.

199
00:23:38,370 --> 00:23:41,510
Thank you! I'll try my best.

200
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:44,430
I'll buy something delicious for us, I have a lot of coupons.

201
00:23:44,430 --> 00:23:46,940
Ah, yes. Thank you.

202
00:23:46,940 --> 00:23:49,740
Your boyfriend is really thoughtful.

203
00:23:49,740 --> 00:23:51,730
It's all thanks to you and Oppa.

204
00:23:51,730 --> 00:23:56,080
Aren't you going to meet Goo Se Joo and Shi Hyun today?

205
00:23:57,400 --> 00:24:02,400
We have to. We have to, but...

206
00:24:04,210 --> 00:24:08,530
Where do you go to meet them? You meet up all the time.

207
00:24:08,530 --> 00:24:13,660
We don't have anywhere to go, so we always go to the park or the cafe.

208
00:24:13,660 --> 00:24:16,770
We had a hideout that only the three of us knew about.

209
00:24:16,770 --> 00:24:20,040
It was more comfortable and warm than our own houses.

210
00:24:20,040 --> 00:24:26,620
That's so cool. Can you invite us there some other time later? I'll keep it a secret.

211
00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:30,050
We'll see.

212
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:34,400
What are you two doing here?

213
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:39,100
What brings you here?

214
00:24:39,100 --> 00:24:44,140
This is by my law firm. Is it just the two of you?

215
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:51,170
- Give it to me, Joo Hwan.
- Alright.

216
00:24:51,170 --> 00:24:53,180
Ah, hello.

217
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:55,320
You're that part-timer at the bar, right?

218
00:24:55,320 --> 00:24:59,940
Hey, Choi Soo Ji. If you're going to go on a date, just go alone. Why did you have to drag Hye Jung here?

219
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:01,770
Don't interfere with what I do and just go.

220
00:25:01,770 --> 00:25:07,770
I'm just saying this because I think it's so sad seeing you dating a nobody and ruining your life.

221
00:25:07,770 --> 00:25:11,880
"A nobody"? "Ruining her life"?

222
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:15,940
Let's go, Hye Jung. This is not a place where an innocent thing like you should be.

223
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:20,290
What's wrong with my Joo Hwn?!

224
00:25:20,290 --> 00:25:24,530
