225
00:25:24,530 --> 00:25:29,650
You must have thrown away your manners or something. There's an extent as to how far I can withstand all your crap.

226
00:25:29,650 --> 00:25:35,000
Look at the color of your shoes! It makes you look so pathetic!

227
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:38,980
Let's go, Joo Hwan. There's no reason for us to listen to all this crap he's saying.

228
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:41,990
- Let's go, Unni.
- Aigoo.

229
00:25:44,600 --> 00:25:49,410
Are you dating someone, Park Hye Jung?

230
00:25:49,410 --> 00:25:52,470
The color of his shoes was really dull. Seriously.

231
00:25:52,470 --> 00:25:54,550
He won't tell your mom about this, right?

232
00:25:54,550 --> 00:25:59,400
There's nothing we can do about it now that it's happened. If I get caught, I'm going to stand up to her.

233
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:03,610
You can't do that since you provoked Ki Young. He's a person that can't stand anything that hurts his pride.

234
00:26:03,610 --> 00:26:06,300
That's right. His personality is seriously...

235
00:26:06,300 --> 00:26:10,550
I saw him fighting at the bar I work at.

236
00:26:10,550 --> 00:26:16,640
You should hurry up and go home, Hye Jung. If Ki Young says anything, just say that Joo Hwan is my boyfriend. You should also so the same, alright?

237
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:18,170
Yes.

238
00:26:18,170 --> 00:26:20,810
Thank you so much, Unni.

239
00:26:20,810 --> 00:26:23,460
Go quickly. Quickly.

240
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:26,100
- I'm leaving.
- I'm leaving.

241
